english: This is the opponent's weak point!

japanese: きっと、聖純女学院でも/楽しくやっていけるさ。
english: I'm sure you can have fun /at Seijun Girls' Academy too.

japanese: きっと、聖純女学院でも/楽しくやっていけるよ。
english: I'm sure you can have fun /at Seijun Girls' Academy too.
Do you want to come back...?

japanese: お願い、いかないで……。/またしばらく、こっちには/これないんでしょ？
english: Please, don't go... /You won't be able to come here /for a while, right?

japanese: こうして皆さんと一緒に、/学園生活を送ることさえ、/任務の一部なのです。
english: Even spending school life /with everyone like this /is part of my mission.
Do you want to come back...?

japanese: この学園祭、/お前は何に注目しているのだ？/参考に聞かせてもらおう。
english: At this festival, /what are you focusing on? /Tell me for reference.

japanese: お疲れさま。/今日は疲れたでしょう。
english: Good work. /You must be tired today.

japanese: この方向でいいですか？
